  <title>Main Menu</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Main Menu</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The main menu is displayed in the top header of the U3Admin web page. As with all user interface elements the menu is responsive to changes in screen size...</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">On larger screen sizes the menu is displayed in full as below...</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="main menu full size.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">On smaller screen sizes the menu is displayed in compact form, the three bars often referred to as a <text style="font-style:italic;">hamburger menu</text>...</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="main menu compact.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Click the <text style="font-style:italic;">hamburger</text> to access the menu...</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="main menu drop down compact.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Menu items are categorised into <text style="font-style:italic;">Menu Groups</text>. Most groups have a title such as Admin, Course, Participation etc. Hover your mouse over groups that do not to discover their title.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
